/*!
	order windows based on an x, y, or (x, y) order
*/

/*!
	order windows based on a creation time order
*/

/*!
	before anything more important, check if wm supports client list property. exit if it does not.
*/

/*!
	choose different font use https://github.com/TheSenatorSteven/microtabber/blob/main/source/microtabber.cold as reference for proper utf8 support
*/

/*!
	use WM_NAME if _NET_WM_NAME does not exist for a given window
*/









